5/files/636c4ab03ffc3de6a90d76900cbd3a95_17ca927a-400c-4302-abb5-2a4324cbb066.jpg?v=1767685789&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/636c4ab03ffc3de6a90d76900cbd3a95_17ca927a-400c-4302-abb5-2a4324cbb066.jpg?v=1767685789&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/636c4ab03ffc3de6a90d76900cbd3a95_17ca927a-400c-4302-abb5-2a4324cbb066.jpg?v=1767685789&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/636c4ab03ffc3de6a90d76900cbd3a95_17ca927a-400c-4302-abb5-2a4324cbb066.jpg?v=1767685789&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/636c4ab03ffc3de6a90d76900cbd3a95_17ca927a-400c-4302-abb5-2a4324cbb066.jpg?v=1767685789&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/636c4ab03ffc3de6a90d76900cbd3a95_17ca927a-400c-4302-abb5-2a4324cbb066.jpg?v=1767685789&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:2.44" width="1464" height="600" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-lmUbDS jhRUAf pf-26_ pf-image-1" store="[object Object]"/></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-27_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-28_ pf-heading-1-h3">Our Story</h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-30_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">PostJoy was born from a fundamental question: What if movement fueled happiness instead of draining it?

We believe the ride isn't just a gap between points A and B. It’s the main event. It's the morning breeze on your face, the effortless climb up a steep hill, the spontaneous detour down a hidden path, and the quiet pride of arriving energized, not exhausted.
</p></div></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-32_"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-33_"><img alt="Our mission" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0975/3316/5885/files/GT28-_1.jpg?v=1767686623&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:2.44" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image5" class="sc-fscnvs dncZrx pf-34_ pf-image-1" store="[object Object]"/></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-35_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-36_ pf-heading-1-h3">Our mission</h3><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-38_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"> To Power Progress, Spark Adventure, and Deliver Pure Joy.</p><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-40_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">We engineer high-performance electric bikes that dissolve the barriers between you and the world. For the urban commuter, we replace stress with sleek, intelligent efficiency. For the weekend explorer, we unlock access to 